### List all Wilders
GET http://localhost:5000/api/wilders

### Get a Wilder by ID

GET http://localhost:5000/api/wilders/1

### Create a Wilder

POST http://localhost:5000/api/wilders
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Jane Doe",
    "city": "Washington, USA"
}

